{"tid":1984700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國總統特朗普：已指示海軍摧毀騷擾美方船隻的伊朗砲艦","createTime":"2020-04-22T15:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T15:58:08.000Z","uid":125193,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cb1129cc962eb670ab2903ae221743754213b579","tid":1984700,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522173-20200422.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522173-20200422.htm&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=f27ada41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522173-20200422.htm&h=32a98f79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522173-20200422.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在社交網站貼文，表示已指示美國海軍摧毀所有在海上騷擾美方船隻的伊朗艦艇。美軍未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普的帖文是在伊朗宣布成功發射軍事衛星後數小時發布。路透社引述伊朗軍方發言人回應，指美國應該專注於抗疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍在上星期表示，有11艘伊朗革命衛隊船隻，在波斯灣的國際水域，靠近並挑釁6艘於該處聯合巡邏的美軍艦艇，雙方最近只是相距9米。"},{"pid":"38be0cc8ead99815a97b9405fe01dd8d2b9b3be6","tid":1984700,"uid":18012,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"應該1粒鐘內<br />\n伊朗海軍就全滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f957e5ddbdb5b0e238ebbeb9f3ad7317ba3b5341","tid":1984700,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"麻煩樓主借一借個位<br />\n各區要人- dse散場派選民登記表(已簡約整合)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1984588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1984588</a>"},{"pid":"40a715614f23722bae05ab8b714643d0c81d3b69","tid":1984700,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T15:39:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/REHTTpfSA